Core Capabilities
- Recovers lost data from multiple file systems including NTFS, FAT, and EXT.
- Supports disk imaging to create exact copies for safe data recovery processes.
- Performs byte-level data recovery from damaged or corrupted storage devices.
- Includes advanced search capabilities to locate files by name or signature.
- Offers RAID reconstruction for complex data recovery scenarios involving multiple disks.

